js-syntax-online

Simple online SQL editor with syntax hightlight in HTML+JavaScript

INSTALL: Copy scripts/ and styles/ to the directory, that contains SQL-Editor.html
Download page for syntax-library: https://github.com/syntaxhighlighter/syntaxhighlighter

This is the answer for

